		</ProjectTile>
		<ProjectTile title="Spotify-Beeper Bot" src={["/projects/spotify.png", "/projects/beeper.png"]} github='https://github.com/Olympicene/spotify-messenger-bot'>
			Beeper bot that when added to a groupchat adds one song to a Spotify playlist per person, per day.
		</ProjectTile>
		<ProjectTile title="Automation-Scripts" src={["/projects/autohotkey.png", "/projects/python.png"]} github='https://github.com/Olympicene/autohotkey-scripts'>
			A Personal selection of Autohokey and python scripts that I currently/have found to be useful
		</ProjectTile>
		<ProjectTile title="Messenger-Stats-CLI" src={["/projects/messenger.png"]} github='https://github.com/Olympicene/messenger-react-counter'>
